collection.name: Space Poggers
collection.description:
# **THE NFT COLLECTION FROM THE FUTURE IS HERE TODAY!**

They were promised booze, ramen, and a rambunctious cruise through the Artemis system aboard The Space Lark. Instead, they got stranded in the smoldering aftermath of a galactic invasion. Pick a tribe, imbibe, and try to survive.

- > Art and character design by [Nate Bear](https://natebear.art/)
- 
- > $MSG Governance Platform allows for community-driven creative democratization
- 
- > Ever-expanding universe of content, media, and lore
- 
- > Featuring [Quantum Metadata](https://quantum.rug.tech) by [RUG.TECH](https://rug.tech) allowing collectors to customize the look of their NFT directly on the collectible
